{"type":"answer","id":2396,"parentType":"question","parentId":546,"uid":902,"contents":"1、膜乎上的“收藏”功能形同虚设，查看不了（已解决）<br>\n<br>\n2、在“编辑回复”中也添加自动保存草稿的功能，以免手滑关掉<br>\n<br>\n3、关于“发布文章”的建议同上<br>\n<br>\n4、“分享”功能也如同虚设，建议在子选项再增一栏”复制链接“，指向自己的答案<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n5、对于已发表的未匿名的答案，可以选择重新匿名<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180502/2e2942439a826907baa70f0c385bdfca.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-01","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}